 Wayne T. Smith is new Chairman and CEO of BASF Corporation 
         










    










 






 











 









Wayne T. Smith is new Chairman and CEO of BASF Corporation

May 01, 2015, 07:00 ET
		  		  					
						 from   BASF Corporation 











 
















































 

 






















































 























 

 

 
 
 
 







Wayne T. Smith becomes new Chairman and CEO of BASF Corporation on May 1, 2015.    
									
