Description

Ep. 698 – In this edition we welcome Dale Smith on board followed by Wayne Madsen. Dale speaks about numerous topics including the Oklahoma City Bombing, 9/11, PizzaGate, and others. Then, Wayne Madsen returns to update us on the research he has been conducting on various topics. First, an update from our UK correspondent Jack Sen.
